### Variables
# @name loadEnv
# @no-cookie-jar
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiSecret = {{$dotenv API_SECRET}}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Extract Fields from PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/extract-fields
Authorization: {{apiSecret}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdf"; filename="test-form.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./src/routes/__tests__/fixtures/test-form.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Fill PDF Form
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/pdf/fill-form
Authorization: {{apiSecret}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdf"; filename="test-form.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./src/routes/__tests__/fixtures/test-form.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="fields"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "txtGeburtsdatum": "15011985"
